title: Winger - Live in Tokyo(1991)
description:
Winger recorded live, Mel Park Tokyo Japan in 1991.  Great live recording, and Reb Beachs' solo is absolutely killer.  Awesome stuff.

Kip Winger - lead vocals, bass, piano
Reb Beach - guitars, backing vocals
Paul Taylor - guitars, keyboards
Rod Morgestein - drums

Tracklist:

01. Intro
02. Madelaine
03. Loosen Up
04. You are the Saint, I am the Sinner
05. Headed for a Heartbreak
06. Without the Night
07. Miles Away
08. Poison Angel
09. Time To Surrender
10. Reb guitar solo
11. Rainbow in the Rose
12. Can't Get Enuff
13. Easy Come Easy Go
14. Hungry
15. Seventeen
